column3:
>INSTALLATION
Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easely built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle, no extra accessories are needed.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts, safety-mounts and heavy-duty gooseneck mounts.

column2:
","

The professional robust car holder The Carcomm Rugged EDA Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your EDA in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your EDA in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user. Safe charging Integrated in the holder is an efficient charging circuit, suitable for 12V and 24V, which powers and charges your EDA. The charger is specially developed for professional use where reliability and quality are very important. The charger keeps your device charged and ready for use in- and outside your vehicle. Protection The cradle is developed to ensure that the EDA is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the EDA firmly seated on the cradle connector while driving on bumpy roads. This also protects the EDA connector and cradle connector from being damaged.

The cradle is developed to ensure that the EDA is kept in place but is still easy to remove. >INSTALLATION
Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easely built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle, no extra accessories are needed.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts, safety-mounts and heavy-duty gooseneck mounts.

column7: &nbsp

column1:
","

The CarComm Rugged EDA Desktop Cradle will charge your Rugged EDA overnight so that it will be ready to go in the morning. The cradle has a robust compact design so that it doesn't take up much deskspace. It's the essential accessory for every professional who uses their Rugged EDA day in day out in the most demanding environments. When the Rugged EDA is placed in the cradle it will start charging and when ready you can simply remove the EDA from the cradle. The included suction- and double sided tape keep the cradle in place, ideal for both small and large EDAs. The cradle comes with an AC adapter which works on 100-240-VAC. The adapter has an EU, UK, US and AUS plug.

Cradle

column7: &nbsp

column1: ","The CarComm Rugged EDA Desktop Cradle will charge your Rugged EDA overnight so that it will be ready to go in the morning. The cradle has a robust compact design so that it doesn't take up much deskspace.
It's the essential accessory for every professional who uses their Rugged EDA day in day out in the most demanding environments.
When the Rugged EDA is placed in the cradle it will start charging and when ready you can simply remove the EDA from the cradle.
The included suction- and double sided tape keep the cradle in place, ideal for both small and large EDAs.

The cradle comes with an AC adapter which works on 100-240-VAC. The adapter has an EU, UK, US and AUS plug.",450.0000,1,"Taxable Goods","Catalog, Search",49.9900,49.9900,,,rugged-eda-desktop-cradle-honeywell-dolphin-6000,"Rugged EDA Desktop Cradle Honeywell Dolphin 6000","Rugged EDA Desktop Cradle Honeywell Dolphin 6000",,,,,,/h/t/httptecpaq.commediacatalogproductcrcrdc-200-honeywell-dolphin-6000.jpg,,,,"11/05/2018, 08:58","29/05/2018, 19:31",,,"Block after Info Column",,,,"Use config",,"12/09/2016, 08:50",,,,,"Use config",,"featured=No,manufacturer=Honeywell,more_product_info=

column1:
52100109,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Passive Cradle Set for Apple iPhone 6 Plus / 6S Plus - Window Installation","

The perfect accessory
The unique and passive holder is the best choice to safely use your mobile device in your vehicle. It's easy to install and comfortable to use. Simply slide-in your device and the holder will keep it firmly in place and when you reach your destination you can
column2:
easily take out your device.

Perfect positioning
column3:
The holder can be positioned perfectly in your vehicle to maximize usability of your device and to reduce reflections on the display. If you don't want to attract unwanted attention when you leave the vehicle, you can easily remove the holder and place it out of sight.

Landscape mode
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Easy installation
column4:
The holder can be placed onto the dashboard or on mounting solutions like a Safety-Mount or Dashmount using the swivel base. Most of the time it is still possible to charge your device, the opening in the bottom allows you to connect a charger so that your device is always ready for use.

","

The professional robust car holder
The Carcomm Passive Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your device in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your mobile device in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user.
column5:
Protection
The cradle is developed to ensure that the device is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the device firmly seated on the cradle while driving on bumpy roads. This also protects the device connector and from being damaged.

52000109,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Passive Cradle Set for Apple iPhone 6 Plus / 6S Plus - Dashboard Installation","

The perfect accessory
The unique and passive holder is the best choice to safely use your mobile device in your vehicle. It's easy to install and comfortable to use. Simply slide-in your device and the holder will keep it firmly in place and when you reach your destination you can
column2:
easily take out your device.

Perfect positioning
column3:
The holder can be positioned perfectly in your vehicle to maximize usability of your device and to reduce reflections on the display. If you don't want to attract unwanted attention when you leave the vehicle, you can easily remove the holder and place it out of sight.

Landscape mode
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Easy installation
column4:
The holder can be placed onto the dashboard or on mounting solutions like a Safety-Mount or Dashmount using the swivel base. Most of the time it is still possible to charge your device, the opening in the bottom allows you to connect a charger so that your device is always ready for use.

","

The professional robust car holder
The Carcomm Passive Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your device in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your mobile device in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user.
column5:
Protection
The cradle is developed to ensure that the device is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the device firmly seated on the cradle while driving on bumpy roads. This also protects the device connector and from being damaged.

Without protection case / bumper case

51010010,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Pass-Through Cradle Set for Apple iPhone 4 / 4S - Dashboard Installation","

The perfect accessory
The unique and passive holder is the best choice to safely use your mobile device in your vehicle. It's easy to install and comfortable to use. Simply slide-in your device and the holder will keep it firmly in place and when you reach your destination you can
column2:
easily take out your device.

Perfect positioning
column3:
The holder can be positioned perfectly in your vehicle to maximize usability of your device and to reduce reflections on the display. If you don't want to attract unwanted attention when you leave the vehicle, you can easily remove the holder and place it out of sight.

Landscape mode
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Easy installation
column4:
The holder can be placed onto the dashboard or on mounting solutions like a Safety-Mount or Dashmount using the swivel base. Most of the time it is still possible to charge your device, the opening in the bottom allows you to connect a charger so that your device is always ready for use.

","

The professional robust car holder
The Carcomm Passive Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your device in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your mobile device in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user.
column5:
Protection
The cradle is developed to ensure that the device is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the device firmly seated on the cradle while driving on bumpy roads. This also protects the device connector and from being damaged.
column7:
Without protection case / bumper case

51010109,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Deluxe Charging Cradle with integrated Antenna Coupler Apple iPhone 6 Plus / 6S Plus / 7 Plus / 8 Plus","

High Quality Apple approved Lightning connector
Keeps the iPhone connector from getting damaged.

Compatible with 12Volt and 24Volt
column2:
Suitable for use in cars and trucks.

Integrated Antenna Coupler
Allows the connection of an external antenna to reduce GSM interference.

e4 Certified
Certified to be used in cars and trucks.

Prepared for permanent installation
Everything is included to hard-wire the cradle into your vehicle.

Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easily built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts and safety-mounts.

","

The Mobile iPhone car cradle allows you to integrate your iPhone in your car.

Perfect fit -
column5:
cradle uses injection molding manufacturing which ensures a perfect fit with your device.

Landscape mode -
column6:
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Antenna Coupler -
column7:
Nowadays very few smartphones have a direct connection for an external antenna. If you want to use an external antenna, the only method is through a passive induction antenna coupler. When you place your device into the cradle, the antenna coupler uses passive induction to transfer the signal between the phone and the coupler, and thus to and from the external antenna.

Safe charging -

column10: >suitable for 12V & 24V
column11:
) which powers and charges your device. This will keep your device charged and ready for use in- and outside your car.

Ready to go -
column12:
The holders are delivered with everything needed to use it right away. Use the window mount to install the holder on your windscreen, plug in the cigarettelgihter adaptor and you are ready to go.

Protection -
column13: The design of the Carcomm Mobile Cradle ensures that your device is protected and sits firmly in the cradle while you are driving. To let the cradle blend in with the interior of your car the color of the cradle matches the dashboard ( dark grey ) with the added bonus that it won&rsquo
column14:

51110108,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Active Charging Cradle for Apple iPhone 6 / 6S","

High Quality Apple approved Lightning connector
Keeps the iPhone connector from getting damaged.

Compatible with 12Volt and 24Volt
column2:
Suitable for use in cars and trucks.

Integrated Antenna Coupler
Allows the connection of an external antenna to reduce GSM interference.

e4 Certified
Certified to be used in cars and trucks.

Prepared for permanent installation
Everything is included to hard-wire the cradle into your vehicle.

Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easily built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts and safety-mounts.

This mount can be installed in a few different ways and here are some illustrations

On the dashboard
This position provides a clear view on the device. The mount can be installed directly on the dashboard and optionally you can also route the cable through the bottom of the mount.

On the dashboard with an overhang
If there isn't enough space between the windscreen and dashboard you can opt for this kind of installation. In this position the
column2: device is hanging partly in front of the dashboard. Optionally you can also route the cable through the bottom of the mount.

column1:
Against the dashboard
If you use a vehicle specific mount or you want to install the mount against the dashboard, you can install the mount in this position. Optionally you can also route the cable through the bottom of the mount.
","The CarComm Dashboard Swivel Mount allows you to mount and use a CarComm Cradle in your vehicle. It provides a convenient way to operate the device and offers a clear view.

43100658,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Deluxe Charging Cradle for Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge","

High Quality Charging Connector
Keeps the mobile device connector from getting damaged.

Compatible with 12Volt and 24Volt
column2:
Suitable for use in cars and trucks.

e4 Certified
Certified to be used in cars and trucks.

Prepared for permanent installation
Everything is included to hard-wire the cradle into your vehicle.

Integrated charging system
By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easily built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts and safety-mounts.

","

The Mobile car cradle allows you to integrate your mobile phone in your car.

Perfect fit -
column5:
cradle uses injection molding manufacturing which ensures a perfect fit with your device.

Landscape mode -
column6:
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Antenna Coupler -
column7:
Nowadays very few smartphones have a direct connection for an external antenna. If you want to use an external antenna, the only method is through a passive induction antenna coupler. When you place your device into the cradle, the antenna coupler uses passive induction to transfer the signal between the phone and the coupler, and thus to and from the external antenna.

Safe charging -
column8: Integrated in the car holder is an efficient charging circuit (
column10: >suitable for 12V & 24V
column11:
) which powers and charges your device. This will keep your device charged and ready for use in- and outside your car.

Ready to go -
column12:
The holders are delivered with everything needed to use it right away. Use the window mount to install the holder on your windscreen, plug in the cigarettelgihter adaptor and you are ready to go.

Protection -
column13: The design of the Carcomm Mobile Cradle ensures that your device is protected and sits firmly in the cradle while you are driving. To let the cradle blend in with the interior of your car the color of the cradle matches the dashboard ( dark grey ) with the added bonus that it won&rsquo
column14:
t attract attention.

Also Fits
Samsung Galaxy S6 SM-G920
Samsung Galaxy J5 SM-J500
Samsung Galaxy A5 2016 SM-A510
Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge SM-G935

column1:
41000658,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/SmartPhones",base,"Passive Cradle Set for Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge","

The perfect accessory
The unique and passive holder is the best choice to safely use your mobile device in your vehicle. It's easy to install and comfortable to use. Simply slide-in your device and the holder will keep it firmly in place and when you reach your destination you can
column2:
easily take out your device.

Perfect positioning
column3:
The holder can be positioned perfectly in your vehicle to maximize usability of your device and to reduce reflections on the display. If you don't want to attract unwanted attention when you leave the vehicle, you can easily remove the holder and place it out of sight.

Landscape mode
If your mobile device supports a landscape mode you can easily rotate the holder into a horizontal position. This is often used while using navigation software on the phone. If you want to use your phone in portrait mode you can easily rotate it back into a vertical position.

Easy installation
column4:
The holder can be placed onto the dashboard or on mounting solutions like a Safety-Mount or Dashmount using the swivel base. Most of the time it is still possible to charge your device, the opening in the bottom allows you to connect a charger so that your device is always ready for use.

","

The professional robust car holder
The Carcomm Passive Cradle is the perfect solution to integrate and use your device in your car. The unique and patented robust design of the active holder keeps your mobile device in place and protects it from being damaged. The perfect holder for the professional user.
column5:
Protection
The cradle is developed to ensure that the device is kept in place but is still easy to remove. This is achieved with special fixtures that keep the device firmly seated on the cradle while driving on bumpy roads. This also protects the device connector and from being damaged.

Compatible with:

column1:
Samsung Galaxy S6 SM-G920
Samsung Galaxy J5 SM-J500
Samsung Galaxy A5 2016 SM-A510
Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge SM-G935

By integrating the charging system into the cradle you can very easily built the cradle into your vehicle. Simply remove the cigarettelighter plug and use the included cable with in-line fuse to hard-wire the cradle into the vehicle.

Installing the cradle
To mount the cradle into the vehicle you can make use of the included rotating swivel-mount. This can be mounted in the vehicle with the included screws. There are also a variety of other mounting solutions available like for example dashmounts and safety-mounts.

column7:

Nowadays very few smartphones have a direct connection for an external antenna. If you want to use an external antenna, the only method is through a passive induction antenna coupler. When you place your device into the cradle, the integrated antenna coupler uses passive induction to transfer the signal between the phone and an external antenna. To make use of the coupler an external antenne has to be connected to the Docking Station.

column1: 54100314,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/CarComm NL,tecpaq/CarComm NL/Multi-Basys",base,"Multi-Basys Cradle CMBS-314 for Apple iPhone 6+ 6S+ 7+ 7S+8+ (All Plus Models)","<table border=""0"">

<td>The main function of the Multi-Basys Cradle is to power and charge your device while you're on the move and to securely hold it in place. The CarComm Multi-Basys is a Universal Vehicle Charging Platform for mobile devices.&nbsp
column2:
The system exists out of two parts, the docking station and the model specific charging cradle.Both parts are only available separately. The compact size of the Multi-Basys system makes it easy to install and it blends in with the car interior.

The unique feature of the CarComm Multi-Basys is that once installed, you can easily swap from device without installing a complete new cradle system. Just swap the model specific charging cradle for a cradle that is compatible with your new phone, slide it into the Docking Station and you are ready to go.
column3: The device cradle can simply be removed from the docking station.

The miniPro fits phone/case combinations from 2.25 In (58mm) to 3.7 In (94mm) wide, and unlimited height. AMPS PLATE,,Default,simple,"tecpaq,tecpaq/iBOLT,tecpaq/iBOLT/Parts",base,"Amps Plate","

The iBOLT Amps plate is developed for users that prefer to have the car-dock attached to a pedestal Mount or vehicle specific mounting solutions from providers like KUDA, ProClip, ProFit etc. The ball joint attaches to the back of any iBOLT designed car-dock and the flat 'plate' screws into the mounting solution. The 4 holes are spaced with the industry standard 32 mm x 38 mm spacing, commonly referred to as 'AMPS' plate. Delivered with double sided tape and 4 small screws with matching small bolts. Allows car-dock to turn either horizontal or vertical. Easy to adjust while driving!

","

Mounting solution includes Amps mount, 2-sided tape, and screws to mount to vehicle specific mounting solutions. The 4 holes are spaced with the industry standard 32mm x 38mm spacing, commonly referred to as 'AMPS' plate.
